addRatings.views.star_rating_form(request)[source]¶

This method is used to get the values from the star rating form to store data of the three types of ratings of each doctor in the database. And it sends email confirmation of ratings submission to the patient.

param request

it’s a HttpResponse from user.

type request

HttpResponse.

return

this method redirects us to another method/def:page that will display the rating form confirmation message.

rtype

HttpResponse.
